cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it deals with the problem of automatically configuring machine learning pipelines. It may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as AutoML is a subfield of AI. Additionally, since the paper deals with image classification tasks, it may belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also involves optimization techniques, which may place it in the sub-categories of cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
